    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just hard to even think about \"navigating\" it. there's nothing left to navigate. when you lose your identity like that, the hole it leaves is just too big. it feels like the only honest thing left to do is just... stop being here. like, why bother trying to fix something that's fundamentally broken?",
